Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嚴肅和睿智的人生中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要和寶貴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有橋牌  高爾夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他們愿意不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都會進威爾特學院的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}降價拋售
