Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.61,0:47:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一加一等于二
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.33,0:48:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二加一等于三
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.20,0:48:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三在M的屋檐下減一
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.97,0:48:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說求方根
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.39,0:48:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是淚水還是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.03,0:48:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是打翻的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.27,0:48:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.23,0:48:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落山了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.59,0:48:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.73,0:48:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.11,0:48:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.07,0:48:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.15,0:48:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個半星期
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.42,0:48:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.92,0:48:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.39,0:49:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在眼睛看不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.57,0:49:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要來到你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.39,0:49:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我數著我的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.03,0:49:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我用破碎的心
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.85,0:49:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了全部的A
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.19,0:49:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會回來嗎  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.05,0:49:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz21.33\pos(187,96)}{\fs15\bord2\be10\shad0\3c&H89CACD&\c&H345558&\fn方正准圆_GBK\b0}愛你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.17,0:49:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找一口井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.70,0:50:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看星星那么的美
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.09,0:50:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因一朵遠不可見的花
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.80,0:50:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而沙漠之所以美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.61,0:50:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為它在某個地方藏著的一口井
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.06,0:50:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看著月光下他那蒼白的額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.02,0:50:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那緊閉的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.89,0:50:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那風中飄動的一縷縷發絲
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.52,0:51:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己說  "我看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.07,0:51:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"只不過是一具驅殼而已"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.90,0:51:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"最重要的東西是用眼睛看不見的"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.42,0:51:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們破曉時找到了那口井
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.01,0:51:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們星球上的人在一個花園里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.39,0:51:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種了上千朵玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.33,0:51:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒找到他們要尋找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.27,0:51:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而他們要找的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.19,0:51:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就在一朵花里
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.98,0:51:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或在一點清水中
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.17,0:52:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  別急
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.23,0:52:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找一口井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.69,0:52:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  聽著  我之前犯了一個大錯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.78,0:52:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再到這兒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.99,0:52:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  這會是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.70,0:52:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -我們去讓飛機起飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.79,0:52:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你要是能在茫茫沙漠中找到一口井
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.88,0:52:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也能找到小王子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.17,0:52:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.22,0:52:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.97,0:52:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.26,0:52:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯  要先把機翼修好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.39,0:52:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.68,0:52:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.37,0:53:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到我要出發的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.52,0:53:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一個人出發
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.44,0:53:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會打擾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.97,0:53:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只占一個小小的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.95,0:53:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.55,0:53:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別丟下我一個人離開
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.29,0:53:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是時候把故事的結局告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.96,0:53:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上  我終于修好了我的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.21,0:53:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我去找小王子
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.17,0:53:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚會去那的  你等著我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.14,0:53:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定你不會讓我受苦很久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.61,0:53:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把它殺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.15,0:53:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  他消失了  溜進了石縫里
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.86,0:53:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.82,0:53:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很顯然  他知道我把發動機修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.21,0:54:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.75,0:54:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要遙遠得多  要困難得多
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.42,0:54:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.43,0:54:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法想象再也聽不到你的笑聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.22,0:54:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  我有一個禮物要送你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.48,0:54:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在天上的某一顆星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.61,0:54:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在其中一顆星星上歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.21,0:54:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次當你在晚上看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.40,0:54:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的星星時
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.67,0:54:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會覺得所有的星星都在歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.33,0:54:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  請不要來
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.71,0:54:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒讓他走吧  你讓他去找那條蛇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.75,0:54:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.26,0:54:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是告別的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.43,0:54:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的  路太遙遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.16,0:55:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這具軀殼太重了  我沒法把它帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.60,0:55:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這就像一副被拋棄的舊軀殼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.64,0:55:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊軀殼并沒那么讓人難過  你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.99,0:55:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到了  就是這里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.58,0:55:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會離開你的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.77,0:55:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.58,0:56:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說他一直在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.12,0:56:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他的玫瑰在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.71,0:56:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.75,0:56:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像他所說的  每晚當我看那些星星時
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.29,0:56:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會聽到他的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.71,0:56:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但你并不能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.51,0:56:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.36,0:56:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能確定的話固然會寬慰很多
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.60,0:56:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不確定的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.82,0:56:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更愿意相信他就在自己的星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.48,0:56:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望當你不在時我也這樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.61,0:56:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我看著星星時
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.39,0:56:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我假裝你并沒有離開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.86,0:56:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.20,0:56:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你用心去看  我會一直與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.43,0:56:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.28,0:56:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.47,0:56:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小王子會一直與他的玫瑰花同在一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.54,0:56:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你并不能完全確定
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.98,0:56:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果他再也沒有找到他的玫瑰花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.03,0:56:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他變成了一個大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.55,0:56:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他孤獨一人呢  如果他迷路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.69,0:56:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他把一切都忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.59,0:57:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我的小姑娘  等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.93,0:57:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小王子永遠不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.47,0:57:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會一直在這里  幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.43,0:57:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要他幫我  我恨小王子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.10,0:57:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小王子  我搞砸了我的整個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.19,0:57:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.90,0:57:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該給我講這么蠢的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.65,0:57:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(192.5,153)}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs25\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\b0\fad(1000,0)}暑假的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.14,0:57:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.86,0:57:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的壞天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.51,0:57:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓32個人上班遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.40,0:58:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交通工具的運輸效率降低了0.4%
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.12,0:58:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.22,0:58:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.18,0:58:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.16,0:58:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.97,0:59:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的  你要干什么  停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.82,0:59:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.24,0:59:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.87,0:59:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.87,0:59:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.83,0:59:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  求您了  請讓我看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.26,0:59:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.21,0:59:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了  他會好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.68,0:59:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  明天是很重要的一天
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.43,1:00:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.89,1:00:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會找到你的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.48,1:02:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會開飛機嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.82,1:02:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  我也有點懷疑
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.32,1:02:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.74,1:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得...我能做到
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.88,1:02:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  幫我保管這個
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.33,1:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我覺得我弄懂這玩意了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.73,1:04:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拉住你了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.29,1:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.67,1:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.51,1:04:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一顆星星嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.47,1:04:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這不是星星
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.04,1:05:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員從來沒有提到過這個地方
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.17,1:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  是他  是他
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.97,1:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.39,1:05:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系好安全帶
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.74,1:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要一個跑道降落
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.75,1:05:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到前面就有一個
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.42,1:05:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好  要著陸了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.68,1:06:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.54,1:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯嘛  快看上面
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.26,1:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從飛機上下來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.64,1:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  從飛機上下來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.19,1:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我  警察先生
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.91,1:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以解釋
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.90,1:06:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手舉起來  舉好
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.03,1:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違規超速  違規變道
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.99,1:07:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非常危險
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.16,1:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.83,1:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闖了好幾個紅燈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.50,1:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.58,1:07:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞公共財產
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.50,1:07:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我一個朋友的朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.49,1:07:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒有見過面
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.00,1:07:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打轉向燈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.22,1:07:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有轉向燈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.00,1:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓他上飛機  帶他回家
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.05,1:07:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架未遂  情況更嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.30,1:07:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記下來  綁架未遂
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.56,1:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  您不是那個...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.39,1:07:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.48,1:07:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛慕虛榮的那個人  就是他
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.11,1:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違抗執法人員
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.76,1:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行公務
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.65,1:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執法人員  我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.95,1:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  您為什么不在自己的星球上
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.25,1:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么這么小
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.25,1:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.75,1:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子是絕不允許出現在這里的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.92,1:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.30,1:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這么快
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.98,1:08:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  非常感謝  繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.62,1:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要喬裝打扮一下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.31,1:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.39,1:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  先生  能借過嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.39,1:09:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忠誠的國民們  上前來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.44,1:09:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是那個國王嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.90,1:09:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-67樓  -很樂意
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.65,1:09:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-27樓  -好的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.45,1:09:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-14樓  -當然
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.74,1:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-142樓  -當然
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.37,1:09:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-34樓  -非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.29,1:09:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.46,1:09:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請按一下天臺
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.04,1:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是說去天臺嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.05,1:09:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當條件很好的時候...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.30,1:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊敬的陛下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.02,1:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  條件很好
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.06,1:09:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下命令
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.71,1:10:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在那
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.60,1:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小王子  小王子
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.31,1:10:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.52,1:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-對不起  -沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.02,1:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的下巴
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.44,1:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒打碎什么吧  -沒有  沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.69,1:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是歇了一小會
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.95,1:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把您認成別人了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.82,1:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.54,1:10:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不會去告發我吧  休息時間結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.08,1:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎  我開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.92,1:10:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作  工作  工作  工作
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.59,1:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去告發我了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.92,1:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信這是他
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.88,1:10:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在該怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.72,1:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子先生
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.14,1:11:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.40,1:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.90,1:11:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.07,1:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想您掉了這個
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.45,1:11:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸牌
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.58,1:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz3.636\pos(223,131)}{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs18\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H614F07&}王子先生
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.74,1:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真倒霉  -真的是他
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.04,1:11:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.91,1:11:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您遇上什么問題了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.62,1:11:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這給我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.87,1:11:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.46,1:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員會不太高興的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.58,1:11:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.42,1:11:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.25,1:11:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把胸牌還給我
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.56,1:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.68,1:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意怎么戴來著
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.39,1:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.59,1:11:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我工作  看到了嗎  我很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.26,1:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  停下  -別和我說話
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.68,1:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道您是誰
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.23,1:11:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是小王子  您害怕猴面包樹
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.40,1:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是王子先生  維修工
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.02,1:11:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕的是生意人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.77,1:11:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在沙漠遇見了飛行員
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.82,1:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給您畫了一只羊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.82,1:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您問題真多
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.82,1:11:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還和遷徙的鳥一起旅行過
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.16,1:11:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開  不好意思  我太忙了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.28,1:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您馴服了一只狐貍  和這只一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.08,1:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒有養過寵物
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.37,1:12:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是寵物  是朋友
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.00,1:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您覺得我有時間交朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.38,1:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要工作
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.67,1:12:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.34,1:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最后一個刷子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.82,1:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我要被炒了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.64,1:12:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最后的機會  太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.89,1:12:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我只是在做我的工作
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.31,1:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-看  這還有一個刷子  -謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.52,1:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我還有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.94,1:12:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  -夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.65,1:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在影響我的效率
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.40,1:12:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有一朵玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.45,1:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一朵什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.74,1:12:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一朵玫瑰  一朵很美的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.91,1:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人驚嘆的玫瑰  她曾獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.12,1:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是...您的蠢話我聽夠了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.50,1:12:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要工作了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.25,1:12:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您都忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.44,1:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您全忘了  -我很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.92,1:12:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很重要的事情要忙
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.38,1:12:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您和他們一樣變成了大人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.59,1:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松開
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.97,1:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.48,1:13:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為什么要這樣  為什么
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.03,1:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系  我不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.74,1:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么好哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.49,1:13:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個大人  大人是不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.12,1:13:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是丟了把刷子嘛  犯不著哭
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.62,1:13:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭也沒用
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.97,1:13:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦擦鼻涕吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.14,1:13:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為什么長得這么矮
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.18,1:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是成年人嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.60,1:13:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  不  我還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.19,1:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也應該是個小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.02,1:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.15,1:14:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩真是太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.24,1:14:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話聽著可不太妙
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.20,1:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道誰能幫你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.91,1:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定這是個好主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.80,1:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子先生  真是稀客啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.64,1:14:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子需要您的幫助
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.02,1:14:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.69,1:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的  我們這兒一般不允許
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.06,1:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶小狗進來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.32,1:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我們可以為您破一次例
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.82,1:14:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣  來  進來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.83,1:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近怎么樣  聊一聊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.04,1:14:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡我的工作  通通煙囪挺好的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.92,1:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  好極了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.93,1:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何非必需品的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.39,1:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都應該變成必需品
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.68,1:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好  王子先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.10,1:15:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看  商人在這兒創造了一件
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.07,1:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么神奇的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.23,1:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們甚至可以把這項創作稱為藝術品
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.74,1:15:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果真這么想  那您就錯了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.91,1:15:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大錯特錯
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.70,1:15:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  任何東西都不能和它相比
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.79,1:15:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的飛機
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.91,1:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項杰作才是最至關重要的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.54,1:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.92,1:15:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等  你怎么能這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.63,1:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過你會幫我的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.96,1:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幫你啊  他們以前就是這么幫我的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.43,1:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(265,86)}{\fn方正书宋_GBK\fs20\b1\bord2\be10\shad0\3c&H7E7C72&\c&H1C1C0F&}畢業照
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.84,1:15:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.60,1:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您總算做了件對的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.23,1:15:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.36,1:15:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您會跟商人說
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.11,1:16:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多么不可或缺的  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.40,1:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會  當然會  我會告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.07,1:16:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商人跟我說  這兒有一份
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.95,1:16:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄著您童年時光的文件
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.74,1:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份文件很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.24,1:16:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這幾張紙完全沒有價值
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.75,1:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  是時候長大了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.38,1:16:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于一切必需品的必備指南
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.34,1:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\frz18.591\pos(194,120)}{\fn方正书宋_GBK\fs13\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H698C83&}關于一切必需品的\N必備指南
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.93,1:16:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能只用一本書
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.90,1:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就概括所有的必需品呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.01,1:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一本非常簡潔的著作
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.91,1:16:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連行距都是單行的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.81,1:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣  您是要我一遍遍讀爛這本書
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.52,1:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我變老嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.19,1:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.98,1:16:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這兒用的是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.41,1:16:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫您快速成長的辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.61,1:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的沒錯吧  王子先生
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.03,1:16:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不重要
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.91,1:16:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看您一臉茫然的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.58,1:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您都忘得一干二凈了  是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.50,1:17:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒  您會覺得自己被夾的有點疼
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.92,1:17:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松  別緊張
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.01,1:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒簽個字
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.47,1:17:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是個簡單的手續
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.35,1:17:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來免除我和商人以及本公司
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.26,1:17:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對本質化過程中可能發生的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.18,1:17:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外死亡或傷殘
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.81,1:17:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所承擔的一切責任
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.44,1:17:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.44,1:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來幫你的  是為了你來的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.86,1:17:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您將會成為一位杰出的大人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.24,1:17:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許碰
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.20,1:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了  不許碰
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.66,1:17:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別像個孩子一樣  王子先生
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.41,1:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了  您可是從我的班級畢業的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.37,1:17:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你們在干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.55,1:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回到您的座位上
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.85,1:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才沖動了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.85,1:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回商人一定會對我失望透頂
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.11,1:18:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  可你為什么救我
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.86,1:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來不知道這是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.57,1:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道它是從哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.41,1:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我跟自己說  這東西可能很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.99,1:18:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你的羊  -我的羊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.00,1:18:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么奇怪的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.50,1:18:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是之前飛行員給你的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.12,1:18:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上的沙漠里給你的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.71,1:18:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-為了吃掉猴面包樹  -這真是災難
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.05,1:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是災難  完全正確
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.76,1:18:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些畫都是飛行員給你畫的
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.26,1:18:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  他很需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.09,1:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  他需要我
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.56,1:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的問題不是長大  而是遺忘
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.73,1:18:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個主意  只要...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.90,1:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的飛機
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.45,1:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  飛機在那兒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.16,1:18:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好它沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.63,1:19:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.57,1:19:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.24,1:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
