Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.85,1:28:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.43,1:28:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們要掉下去了
