Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.75,1:28:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.11,1:29:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來  快看  我找到它了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.99,1:29:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.33,1:29:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.50,1:29:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.49,1:30:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.46,1:30:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.43,1:30:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.61,1:30:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本來應該和她重逢的
