Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.91,1:30:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去他
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.08,1:30:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.30,1:31:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么忍住不哭的
